<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 09:13:14 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>消息人士称，必和必拓顾问正在征求投资者对改善英美资源集团出价的看法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/bhp-adviser-canvassing-investor-views-improved-anglo-bid-sources-say-2024-04-29/</link><description>消息人士称，必和必拓在其 390 亿美元收购案中的顾问正在征求部分股东的意见，该公司在上周最初的提议被拒绝后正在考虑提出修改后的报价。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 08:53:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/bhp-adviser-canvassing-investor-views-improved-anglo-bid-sources-say-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>拜登签署台湾和TikTok立法后，中国暗示将进行报复</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-hints-retaliation-after-biden-signs-taiwan-tiktok-legislation-2024-04-29/</link><description>中国周一暗示，在美国总统乔·拜登签署加强台湾防御的法律并寻求让 TikTok 的中国所有者从该社交媒体平台撤资后，中国可能会进行报复。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 08:49:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-hints-retaliation-after-biden-signs-taiwan-tiktok-legislation-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国农业银行一季度利润下降1.63%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-agbank-posts-163-fall-q1-profit-2024-04-29/</link><description>中国农业银行 (AgBank) 周一公布第一季度净利润下降 1.63%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 08:43:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-agbank-posts-163-fall-q1-profit-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国将对美国部分产品的进口关税豁免期限延长至11月30日</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-extend-tariff-exemptions-imports-some-us-products-until-nov-30-2024-04-29/</link><description>中国财政部周一在一份声明中表示，中国将对部分美国产品的进口关税豁免期限延长至11月30日。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 08:26:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-extend-tariff-exemptions-imports-some-us-products-until-nov-30-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>什么是特斯拉的全自动驾驶以及为什么其在中国的推出很重要</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/what-is-teslas-full-self-driving-why-its-china-rollout-matters-2024-04-29/</link><description>据知情人士透露，特斯拉首席执行官埃隆·马斯克周日抵达北京进行一次未经宣布的访问，预计他将讨论全自动驾驶（FSD）软件的推出以及向海外传输数据的许可。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 08:21:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/what-is-teslas-full-self-driving-why-its-china-rollout-matters-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平将访问法国、塞尔维亚和匈牙利，旨在促进欧盟关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xi-visit-france-serbia-hungary-may-5-10-foreign-ministry-says-2024-04-29/</link><description>中国国家主席习近平将于5月5日至10日访问法国、塞尔维亚和匈牙利，这是他五年来的首次欧洲之行，旨在在与世界第二大经济体的紧张局势加剧之际促进欧盟关系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 07:41:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xi-visit-france-serbia-hungary-may-5-10-foreign-ministry-says-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>农化公司先正达第一季度销售额和盈利大幅下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/agrochemicals-company-syngenta-posts-big-drop-q1-sales-earnings-2024-04-29/</link><description>种子和农药制造商先正达周一表示，第一季度销售额和利润大幅下降，就在这家瑞士公司搁置其 100 亿美元上市计划几周后。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 06:08:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/agrochemicals-company-syngenta-posts-big-drop-q1-sales-earnings-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示中国四月份工厂活动扩张速度可能放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-april-factory-activity-likely-expanded-slower-speed-2024-04-29/</link><description>路透社周一的一项调查显示，中国四月份的制造业活动可能会放缓，这表明该国庞大的工厂部门可能在第二季度初失去了一些动力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 05:49:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-april-factory-activity-likely-expanded-slower-speed-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国房地产股因刺激计划而上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinese-property-shares-rally-stimulus-hopes-2024-04-29/</link><description>中国房地产开发商的股价周一上涨，因市场猜测本周可能会出台更多刺激措施，旨在清理库存、促进销售和取消购房限制。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 05:47:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinese-property-shares-rally-stimulus-hopes-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，台湾经济第一季度因出口强劲而增长5.6%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwans-economy-seen-expanding-56-first-quarter-strong-exports-2024-04-29/</link><description>路透社周一的一项民意调查显示，由于对人工智能（AI）应用技术的需求乐观，出口反弹，台湾依赖贸易的经济可能在第一季度增长更快。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 05:03:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwans-economy-seen-expanding-56-first-quarter-strong-exports-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，百度与特斯拉就 FSD 在中国的地图绘制交易达成一致</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/baidu-tesla-agree-mapping-deal-fsd-china-sources-say-2024-04-29/</link><description>两位知情人士称，中国主要互联网搜索公司百度与特斯拉达成协议，授予该汽车公司在中国公共道路上收集数据的测绘许可证。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 04:24:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/baidu-tesla-agree-mapping-deal-fsd-china-sources-say-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>彭博新闻社称，特斯拉与百度的交易扫清了中国辅助驾驶领域的关键障碍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tesla-clears-key-china-assisted-driving-hurdle-with-baidu-deal-bloomberg-news-2024-04-29/</link><description>据彭博社周一报道，特斯拉将通过与百度合作开发地图和导航功能，扫清在中国推出先进辅助驾驶功能的关键障碍。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 04:14:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tesla-clears-key-china-assisted-driving-hurdle-with-baidu-deal-bloomberg-news-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国房地产开发商佳兆业清算听证会延期至5月27日</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-property-developer-kaisas-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-may-27-2024-04-29/</link><description>香港一家法院将佳兆业集团清算听证会推迟至 5 月 27 日，这家陷入困境的中国房地产开发商表示，其目标是在未来 4 周内敲定重组条款。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 03:48:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-property-developer-kaisas-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-may-27-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国将向月球“隐藏”的一面发起高风险任务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/china-set-launch-high-stakes-mission-moons-hidden-side-2024-04-29/</link><description>中国将在未来几天内发射一艘机器人航天器往返月球背面，这是三项技术要求很高的任务中的第一项，这将为中国首次载人登陆和在月球南极建立基地铺平道路。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 03:23:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/china-set-launch-high-stakes-mission-moons-hidden-side-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>马斯克访问期间，特斯拉清除了中国自动驾驶的关键监管障碍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/boss-battery-giant-catl-visits-elon-musks-hotel-beijing-reuters-witness-2024-04-29/</link><description>特斯拉已经清除了一些长期阻碍其在中国推出自动驾驶软件的关键监管障碍，为埃隆·马斯克出人意料地访问这家美国汽车制造商第二大市场并取得良好成果铺平了道路。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 03:06:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/boss-battery-giant-catl-visits-elon-musks-hotel-beijing-reuters-witness-2024-04-29/</guid></item></channel></rss>